        Christian Goudreau
        <br/>
        <ui:msg description="Our Team > Chris Goudreau > Position">Co-Founder / CEO</ui:msg>
        <br/>
        <p>
            <ui:msg description="Our Team > Chris Goudreau > Bio">Over the last five years, Christian was lead developer
                for different companies to design many Web
                applications based on the Cloud. Other than his passion for development and software engineering,
                Christian
                is self-ta ught and his involvement is directly linked to the success of several open-source projects
